{"word":"ἄφορος","slug":"ἄφορος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἄφορος</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:φέρω'><el>φέρω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>not bearing, barren</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>causing barrenness, blighting</i>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}